messages.install: <center>Thanks for installing the DNS Techpack for Minecraft 1.10.2! Have fun!</center>
messages.update: Please read the changelog, or you may lose some of your things. Otherwise, have fun!

warnings.warnSponge:
Sponge is currently in a BETA state.

When reporting an issue you must state that you are using sponge!
warnings.warnTechReborn:
TechReborn changes the recipes of items from other mods.

This mod is very similar to old GregTech and is not for the faint-hearted.

mods.name: Compact Solar Arrays
mods.description: Compact Solar Arrays, an Industrial Craft 2 mod that adds in three new Solar Panel type blocks: Solar Arrays. Solar Arrays condense 8 (Low Voltage), 64 (Medium Voltage) or 512 (High Voltage) Industrial Craft 2 solar panels into a single block. This significantly reduces the CPU impact of large amounts of Solar Energy gathering so is a common server enhancement. New in 4.0: Solar Hats- charge armor at the same rate as their block counterparts would
